@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - Madtorio</PageTitle>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>About Madtorio</h1>
    <p>Learn about our community and what drives us to build, share, and optimize.</p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
        <h2>Our Community</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>
            Madtorio is a vibrant Factorio community dedicated to building, sharing, and optimizing factories.
            Whether you're a beginner looking to learn the basics or a veteran seeking to push the limits
            of automation, you'll find like-minded engineers here.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our community focuses on collaboration, knowledge sharing, and the relentless pursuit of efficiency.
            From megabases to speedruns, from vanilla builds to heavily modded creations, all playstyles are welcome.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h3>Save Files & Knowledge</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>
                    Browse and download save files from community members. Learn from expert factory designs,
                    discover new building techniques, and get inspired for your next project.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We believe in the power of shared knowledge. Members regularly share blueprints, tutorials,
                    and insights gained from countless hours of factory building.
                </p>
                <a href="/downloads" class="btn">Browse Downloads</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h3>Discord Community</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>
                    Join our active Discord server to connect with other players, ask questions, share your builds,
                    and participate in community events.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our members are always happy to help newcomers and discuss advanced optimization strategies.
                </p>
                <a href="https://tinyurl.com/madtorio-server" target="_blank" class="btn">Join Our Discord</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>The Factory Must Grow</h2>
            </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>
            In Factorio, we learn that the factory must always grow. At Madtorio, we apply the same philosophy
            to our community. We're always looking for new members, new ideas, and new ways to optimize our
            collective factory-building experience.
        </p>
        <p>
            Join us, and let's grow together!
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
    </div>
</div>

